<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
At everydaymoneylab, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices available to you.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<p>
We may collect information that you voluntarily provide, such as your name or email address when you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us. We may also collect limited technical information such as browser type, device information, IP address, and pages visited for analytics and website performance.
</p>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>

<ul>
<li>To improve our website and content.</li>
<li>To respond to inquiries and reader feedback.</li>
<li>To send newsletters or updates if you subscribe.</li>
<li>To understand how visitors use our website.</li>
<li>To maintain website security and performance.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Cookies</h2>

<p>
Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to improve user experience, remember preferences, analyze website traffic, and support advertising services. You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>
We may use trusted third-party services such as analytics providers, advertising partners, email marketing platforms, and affiliate programs. These services may collect information according to their own privacy policies.
</p>

<h2>Advertising</h2>

<p>
As everydaymoneylab grows, we may display advertisements provided by advertising partners such as Google AdSense or other advertising networks. These partners may use cookies or similar technologies to deliver relevant advertisements.
</p>

<h2>Affiliate Links</h2>

<p>
Some pages may contain affiliate links. If you purchase through these links, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. Please see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more information.
</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>

<p>
We take reasonable measures to protect information collected through our website. However, no method of transmitting or storing information over the internet is completely secure.
</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>

<p>
Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including the ability to request access, correction, or deletion of your data where applicable.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>

<p>
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be published on this page with the updated revision date where appropriate.
</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<p>
If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/contact/">Contact</a> page.
</p>

